728311f-a.title: Richmond: Amboy Road - Annadale Road
728311f-a.text:
Amboy Road, north side, at its junction with Annadale Road,
showing the Annadale Hotel. It belonged to A. Britton (1874 to
1887), and later (1898) to Wm. Smith. Still later it was the
property of Mrs. 1L. Stacker (1907). The dates refer to maps on
which the owners' names appear.
1923.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
